reviews: I love this toque, I've worn it everywhere. I had to stretch it out over the headrest of my computer chair the first night I got it, but after that it's fit my big head great. This is not the "fashion" version of the toque but honestly I've found no difference in how it looks on your head. It's still nice and long so there's that empty space at the top of the head and it just looks really nice (plus it's warm!).

review_title: Never going back to official refills
reviews: These work perfectly, and are such a good deal. There was an error when you first load them but you just exit that popup and you're good to go after.

Our 6yo girls had these shoes and wore them everywhere. They can get them on and off really quickly and had no issues with the velcro wearing out. They can also easily be rinsed off. Very durable and high quality product, now I'm buying them for our 2yo.

Love these gates, I have 3! The plastic lattice does give a little when pushed on, which I think is safer then if it were to be brittle. There's no way a small person would be strong enough to break through it.
Good for the price, and I assembled it basically by myself. The only downside is that the drawers are slightly skewed.

review_title: Sturdy and can't tell it's anything different
reviews: For those of you wondering, yes it fits inside a queen bed frame. The slats on my frame broke so I took them out, and popped this thing in. Sturdy and can't tell it's anything different. But yes, watch your feet when you make the bed, the middle support foot is never where you expect it to be.

review_title: Not a bad chair, the seat is huge I can cross ...
reviews: Not a bad chair, the seat is huge I can cross my legs while sitting. The lumbar curve is also decent. Weak points are that the seat cushion has firmed up quite a bit now, the wheels aren't spinning as smoothly as they used to and the left armrest has broken off. Overall decent design but not incredibly durable.

review_title: My nose was having a really bad reaction to the ring that I was pierced with
reviews: My nose was having a really bad reaction to the ring that I was pierced with, but when I switched out for this ring it finally healed praise the lord! So that's enough for me to know it's a genuine product as advertised.

review_title: For a nice flush close you could only get away with like ...
reviews: I have a very hard time closing this wallet when it is filled with cards as shown in the picture. For a nice flush close you could only get away with like 2 or 3 cards. It seems like this set up would be very convenient but really it just makes things more awkward.
